description: Rizzo Group AB owns and operates shoe and accessory stores. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 387 full-time employees.  The Company’s activities are divided into two business areas: Accessories and Shoes and has three own brands: Accent, Morris, Rizzo and departments at Nordiska Kompaniet (NK) with own and external brands. The Accessories area is responsible for operating the Accent and Morris store chains and the Shoes business area operates of own (Rizzo) and external brands. Furthermore, the Company operates approximately 101 stores in Sweden and Norway.
name: Rizzo Group AB
